text: Rumah Sait is a settlement in the Kanowit division of Sarawak, Malaysia. It lies approximately east of the state capital Kuching. Neighbouring settlements include: *Wuak east *Rumah Jambai northeast *Rumah Tumal northeast *Rumah Rii north *Rumah Buyong southwest *Rumah Penghulu Gara southwest *Rumah Nyumbang southeast *Rumah Nyawai southeast *Rumah Penghulu Linau northeast *Rumah Jilan south ==References== Category:Populated places in Sarawak
title: Rumah Sait
